org.radarcns.management.config

Class LocalKeystoreConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.radarcns.management.config.LocalKeystoreConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.radarcns.auth.config.ServerConfig

    public class LocalKeystoreConfig
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.radarcns.auth.config.ServerConfig
    Radar-auth server configuration for using a local keystore. This will load the MP public key from our keystore, no need to make an HTTP call to ourselves to fetch it.
